text: Manuëla “Maan” Kemp (13 February 1963 – 17 January 2025) was a Dutch singer and television presenter. Kemp was the television presenter of among others Nationale Postcode Loterij within the quiz programm De 64.000 gulden vraag, Eigen Huis & Tuin, Wie-O-Wie, Twee Vrouwen op Stap in..., Maan bij Nacht, and De vrienden van Amstel LIVE!. In April 2000 she was in the Dutch Playboy magazine. On 7 December 2024, Kemp was seriously injured in a scooter accident in Loulé, Portugal. She stayed at a hospital in Faro in a coma with serious brain damage. After moved to the Netherlands she died on 17 January 2025 at the Tergooi Hospital in Hilversum at the age of 61. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:2025 deaths Category:Dutch singers Category:Dutch television presenters Category:People from North Holland
